# LAB-WIN-014 — Microsoft Defender Antivirus Policy
 
## Objective
 
Configure Microsoft Defender Antivirus using Intune Endpoint Security.
 
---
 
## Navigation Path
 
Intune Admin Center  
Endpoint security → Antivirus
 
---
 
## Step-by-Step
 
1. Open Intune Admin Center
 
2. Navigate to:
 
Endpoint security → Antivirus
 
3. Create policy
 
4. Configure:
 
Real-time protection → Enabled  
Cloud-delivered protection → Enabled
 
5. Assign to:
 
INT-WIN-Enrolled-Devices
 
